Solution comprises following four files


1. ec2-web-create.yml (ansible playbook)
2. inv (inventory ini file)
3. key.yml (encrypted key file)
4. variables.yml (variables for playbook)
5. index.php (php webpage)


In this version key file is encrypted and variables separated out

To run the playbook use following command

ansible-playbook ec2-web-create.yml --vault-id trialproj@passvault

[** passvault {password file} will be sent separately** ]
